Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是2D4  即将进入东京租界管辖领空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解  飞行目的是宣传活动  没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此毫无变更
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滞空时间也与申报一样  预计为14小时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确认  批准进行高空飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此次通话深表感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去曾跟随Zero  威振布列塔尼亚的黑之骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现今只剩下在座几位了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在谈绝望还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这次的「飞燕4号」作战能够成功的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本  万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本  万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗  您还真是穷追不舍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可别想逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  下次再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副会长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你想靠体力决胜那一刻起  你就已经输了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会太小题大作了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是堂体育补课而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就给我好好去上课
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑齐学分应该是不成问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是普通的上色气体罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  副会长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这也算学生会长么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  不由得就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想杀了我吗  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪巴鲁  是什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪巴鲁  这个我就借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路真是的  又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Turn 01\N魔神复苏之日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  至少希望放学后能有点自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  都怪哥哥专门翘课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种课多无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰劳你的  会长给的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离Zero引发的叛乱事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「黑色暴动」的镇压  马上就1年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个Area 11也完全恢复平静了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然事件当时有很多传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们兄弟俩也曾考虑过是否要回到布列塔尼亚本土去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志愿调查表你交掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蕾塔老师不是在生气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上大学么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生这身份已经当厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说  受人摆布还真是让人不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这也无济于事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:05:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使进入社会  头顶上坐着的  照样还是那些大企业和贵族们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发展完全了的社会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是大人构筑的等级社会中一枚棋子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是在歧视你们Eleven  而是在区分你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven被Zero这个骗子所摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想做回日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是极其好战又危险的人种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此不得不由我们布列塔尼亚来进行强化管理和教育
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven人输了  是因为势单力薄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能守本份的话  也不用被贬在「矫正教育区」里的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero  真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什么  反正世界也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快点  卡纳雷斯总督
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中华联邦的使节们已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  机情局的作战如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\an8}（机情局：机密情报局）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  在巴比伦塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在今天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下究竟作何考虑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今黑之骑士团的残党已经不足为惧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且Zero也已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许偷懒  Eleven的懒猴子们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标已经到达  跟预想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由B3进入第5大门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次总该出现了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出现就白费心机了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经把扩展到租界外延部分的风险都计算进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来只要送我来就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的又是非法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是校方教育辅导处分  就能了事的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区的警察…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥不缺钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想和更厉害的对手交手罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是谎话  做这种事只不过想打发无聊的时间而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天进行的是引入注目的兄弟对决
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侥幸存活的将会是哥哥  还是弟弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场比赛  对于连中10回合的客人  将送出7点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  回去吧  这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系  一目了然不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  在享乐的是我们布列塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被玩弄和工作的是Eleven
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然装作视而不见  其实本质上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven输了两次  枢木首相的那一次和Zero的那次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明毫无力量还搞什么叛乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Eleven
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是布列塔尼亚的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就越发不该这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很讨厌将标榜所谓的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  弱者必须忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使对方有错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别把你们的价值观强加与我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我看看你的脸么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下今天的兔女郎狩猎  真是收获丰富呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是货物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是货物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战败的人就是没有权利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常事态  发生纠纷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你就好好后悔  自身的无力吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下不也是这么说的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱肉强食  这就是世界的法则
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  他们可是黑帮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话真是傲慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自认为是享用的一方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位同学  这可是大人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  大人的世界和学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底会是谁吃谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且就用这个来分个高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用国际象棋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生真是不知天高地厚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不尽然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗之王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界也是相当有名的赌徒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  知道我的名号还来挑战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果Zero在的话  怎会被你们这些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  别再提那个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero才不是什么叛徒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有什么难言之隐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难言之隐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终决战  指挥官疏忽职守还能有什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  Zero已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗之王居然会这么简单就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吃掉的可是你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种传闻如果传出去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就颜面扫地了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没兴趣到处宣扬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了  学生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在说你设下的老千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出老千？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个坏孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国际象棋怎么可能出老千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  接下来就得伪造证据了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是阴险狡诈的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公正的事情  并没有价值啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然使用飞行船  这是你们最后的挣扎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机密情报局  Valhalla7号行动  开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到Area 11
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们如此隆重的迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说Zero已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero  不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中华联邦的诸位若是想理解我们布列塔尼亚的话  为时过早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…  说的这么直截了当  真是让我大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把腰间之物交给我们保管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治安万无一失  那种古董就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻  这样太无礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是说到能够理解我们中华联邦的话  似乎为时过早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  目标跟丢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我们也冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:13:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击巴比伦塔的恐怖分子好像拥有数架Knight Mare
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始之际  周边管制完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  进入第七步骤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长  卡纳雷斯总督…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方的官吏无视就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是受皇帝陛下之命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven给我走楼梯去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之骑士团的残党为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布列塔尼亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的布列塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我没能好好抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  现在卜部他们正在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的Knight Mare
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是  要把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  绝对能逃出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会想办法让你逃出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路真是的  把罗洛也拖进去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老实说吧  很担心鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗…罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一定要救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭我的能力把唯一的弟弟救出来还是能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我  这点能力还是有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  连Eleven都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还执念于Zero这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想杀了我吗  怎么办  就算逃跑也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接你了  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的敌人是布列塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是定了契约吗  我们是共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约？  共犯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我知道  真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的  我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布列塔尼亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  还有人活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的使命完成了  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修·兰佩鲁吉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使命？  你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在观察你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6点59分起床
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7点12分和弟弟一起边看新闻边吃早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视听内容上并无偏颇言论思维
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8点54分到校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出席早班会和第一节课  而在屋顶看书
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二节的物理课…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今天的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似驯养日记之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为诱饵的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱饵？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说陷阱也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了引诱出那个魔女C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是个男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再和低贱的诱饵会话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  到处理的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就没有目击者了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们  就这么完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不知道就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么简单的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃离这里的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能与世界抗衡的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音  刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到力量  你早已经拥有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被封印在忘却的牢笼中罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「王」的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就解开封印吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那些在生活中如荆棘般刺痛我的焦躁不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  全部都是虚假的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是Zero！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修  我不会乞求你的原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的回答吗  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在处理我之前  希望你能回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明击穿了心脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果无力即是邪恶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量就是正义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇是否是邪恶  友情算得上是正义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有邪恶正义之分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱饵只有「死」这一个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那么你们就留下这段事实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修·Vi·布列塔尼亚  在此命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们  去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起  我的心就有一个疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相吻合的虚假生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏离的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被移植了另一片记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴役般的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  真相一直追寻着我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  错的不是我  是世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界可以改变  我来改变它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了  Zero大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我们下达命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我就是Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个破坏世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造世界的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让别人抢先的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死Zero的  将是本人


